{"tid":1884840,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"陳帆做完show 傾倒[漂白水]入水渠","createTime":"2020-02-18T00:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T13:21:42.000Z","uid":121112,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f7c6a39602e0ada2a061a3481b280ad0ad75544e","tid":1884840,"uid":121112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T00:48:58.000Z","msg":"【齊心抗疫】的士及小巴業界今日在中環愛丁堡廣場舉行「的士小巴抗疫大行動」啓動禮，推出可持續的抗疫措施，包括在港島、九龍及新界的12個專用石油氣站，向業界司機派發「抗疫愛心包」，內有消毒噴霧劑一枝，醫護口罩乙個及抗疫單張。同時，全港亦會設立多個補充點，司機可以補充用完的清潔劑。運輸及房屋局局長陳帆、民政事務局副局長陳積志、運輸署署長陳美寶等亦有出席活動，期間一眾官員一同清潔的士、小巴車廂。活動完成後，有人將兩桶標籤為「漂白水」的液體倒進水渠作處理。（張浩維攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Dp5rw4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Dp5rw4.jpg&h=37843485&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rF7KG5q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrF7KG5q.jpg&h=ae35c42c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Z1odb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Z1odb6.jpg&h=c670113c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9ywSQYN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ywSQYN.jpg&h=68e1609a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9VMLrw8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9VMLrw8.jpg&h=bb9969c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TvPw6w9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTvPw6w9.jpg&h=f1c75a4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#01影像 #紀實 #武漢肺炎 #運輸業 #陳帆 #漂白水<br />\n<br />\nFrom 01影像facebook"},{"pid":"32a3e4051c2dd1331fbdb31df4ea02e495cd73a7","tid":1884840,"uid":127695,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T00:50:30.000Z","msg":"污水倒落雨水渠？"},{"pid":"12a28ae7e76e122fb0f9f6478b86248e50cd5d06","tid":1884840,"uid":34970,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"f7c6a39602e0ada2a061a3481b28